Footer and header show catalogs

GET /
1. Catalogs
1.1. The most cheap price attached to each catalog
2. Reviews
3. Certificates, thanks

GET /catalogs, /catalog
1. Catalogs
2. Five the most famous sub-catalogs (like chidren's furniture can be splitted to children's beds, tables; bathroom can be splitted to mirrors, baths, toilets)

GET /catalogs/{catalog}, /catalog/{catalog}
1. All sub-catalogs
2. About 40-50 the most famous products (probably rate popularity by hits)
Parameters:
1. Parameters from different categories intersect (red AND for kids AND made in China AND manufacturer is ChinaChairs inc.)
2. Parameters from the same category unite((red OR blue OR green) AND (made in China OR in USA OR in Sweden))
